ctu.nengoros.comm.rosBackend.encoders

Interface MultiTerminationEncoder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Resettable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MultiTerminationEncoderImpl

    public interface MultiTerminationEncoder
extends Resettable

    Compared to BasicEncoder, this is not a Termination, but can have multiple Terminations, whose values are combined into single value published on a single ROS topic.

    One MultiTerminationEncoder is initialized with one own Termination. If this Termination is already used, the new one, free one, should be simple added.

    TODO: only one dimensional Terminations are supported so far. TODO: use methods for Termination to setup parameters all own Terminations at once (e.g. setTau..)
